ight:16px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"padding:0px;border:0px;list-style:none;word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:normal;font-family:menlo;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\">}</p></div><div style=\"font-family:宋体, verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">使用时：</div><div style=\"font-family:宋体, verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\"><p style=\"padding:0px;border:0px;list-style:none;word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:normal;font-family:menlo;color:#2E595D;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:21px;color:#40207C;\">NSLog</span><span style=\"word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:21px;color:#000000;\">(</span><span style=\"word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:21px;color:#D62C24;\">@\"set&nbsp;count:%d\"</span><span style=\"word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:21px;color:#000000;\">,[myBook</span>&nbsp;countofCardsInSet<span style=\"word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:21px;color:#000000;\">]);</span><span style=\"word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:21px;color:#008324;\">//</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;font-family:\'heiti sc light\';color:#008324;\">元素个数</span></p></div><div style=\"font-family:宋体, verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">注意：如果多次加入同一对象，那么set中的总数不会增加，而是该对象的retain增加。</div><div style=\"font-family:宋体, verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:30px;font-family:simsun;font-size:20px;\"><strong>遍历<span style=\"word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:normal;font-family:menlo;color:#00B3F9;\">NSMutableSet</span>中元素：</strong></span></div><div style=\"font-family:宋体, verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\"><p style=\"padding:0px;border:0px;list-style:none;word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:normal;font-family:menlo;color:#008324;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\">&nbsp;<wbr></p><p style=\"padding:0px;border:0px;list-style:none;word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:normal;font-family:menlo;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\">-&nbsp;(<span style=\"word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:21px;color:#C02D9D;\">void</span>)printBookForSet{</p><p style=\"padding:0px;border:0px;list-style:none;word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:normal;font-family:menlo;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\">&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;<span style=\"word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:21px;color:#C02D9D;\">for</span>&nbsp;(<span style=\"word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:21px;color:#4B8186;\">AddressCard</span>&nbsp;*theCard&nbsp;<span style=\"word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:21px;color:#C02D9D;\">in</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:21px;color:#4B8186;\">_bookSet</span>)&nbsp;{</p><p style=\"padding:0px;border:0px;list-style:none;word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:normal;font-family:menlo;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\">&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;[theCard&nbsp;<span style=\"word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:21px;color:#2E595D;\">print</span>];</p><p style=\"padding:0px;border:0px;list-style:none;word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:normal;font-family:menlo;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\">&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;}</p><p style=\"padding:0px;border:0px;list-style:none;word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:normal;font-family:menlo;min-height:16px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\">&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;&nbsp;<wbr></p><p style=\"padding:0px;border:0px;list-style:none;word-wrap:normal;word-break:normal;line-height:normal;font-family:menlo;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\">}</p></div><div style=\"font-family:宋体, verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;line-height:1.5;\">使用时：</div><div style=\"font-